==Trivia== *The album art is a parody of Nirvana's album Nevermind. *In the "FairlyOdd Parents" episode "One Man Banned" there is a scene where it shows Timmy Turner on albums covers.&nbsp; One of these albums is "Off the Deep End". *The Song Waffle King Was Suposed To Be On This Album, But Was Moved To Alapalooza
===Easter eggs=== After the last song, there are ten minutes of dead silence. After the ten minutes are over the song [[Song:Bite Me|Bite Me]] starts playing. This hidden track was put in to parody Nirvana's "Endless Nameless" and to scare listeners who forgot to turn the CD player off. It lasts about 6 seconds.
