==Trivia==
* This is the biggest [["Weird Al" Yankovic|Al]] album, being the only one with four discs.
* Al hand picked the tracks to include on this compilation from his 8 [[Studio Albums (info)|Studio Albums]] he had produced at the time.
*Permanent Record includes [[Happy Birthday (Placebo EP version)|the Placebo EP version]] of [[Happy Birthday]], the Capitol Records single version of [[My Bologna]] and the [[UHF (Single Version)|single version of UHF.]]

