''This page is about the band "Al's Band." To view other pages, see [[Al's Band (disambiguation)]].''

'''Al's Band''' is a band started by [["Weird Al" Yankovic|Weird Al]]'s band mates, [[Steve Jay]], [[Jon "Bermuda" Schwartz]], [[Rubén Valtierra]], and [[Jim West]].

