These are the visuals that occur during the music video for the song [[Skipper Dan]].
{| border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=5 style="border-collapse:collapse" |- bgcolor=#6633FF ! Visuals !! Lyrics |- | A man wakes up from bed and hits his alarm clock, which reads "6:00" || |- | Walks by a picture of himself acting || I starred in every high school play |- | Zooms in on picture, it turns to color and shows him acting. || Blew every drama teacher away |- | Shows people clapping then cuts to the man graduating. || Graduated first in my class at Julliard |- | Zooms out and the picture becomes black and white again and it turns into a picture hanging on the mans wall. He walks by while brushing his teethe. || Took every acting workshop I could |- | The man opens his blinds to reveal the Hollywood sign || And I dreamed of Hollywood |- | Toothepaste falls from the mans face next to a playbill of "Cat on a Hot Tin Roof" || While I read my Uta Hagen, and studied the Bard |- | Zooms into playbill to show him acting again || Picked up parts and paid my dues And got phenomenal rave reviews |- | Shows the man signing autographs || I knew the world was gonna love me, without a doubt |- | Shows the man on his bed looking at a poster || I was sure that Tarantino would be calling me on my phone Annie Liebowitz would shoot me for Rolling Stone |- | He looks in the mirror || But the years have come and gone and I'm sorry to say That's not the way that it's all worked out |- | It fades to him wearing a Jungle Cruise outfit on the cruise boat || I'm a tour guide on the Jungle Cruise ride Skipper Dan is the name And I'm doing 34 shows every day, and every time it's the same |- | Dan points to some hippos as the swim by || Look at those hippos, they're wiggling their ears Just like they've done for the last 50 years Now I'm laughing at my own jokes, but I'm crying inside |- | Shows Dan laughing a bit as his smile turns to a frown || 'Cause I'm working on the Jungle Cruise ride |- | Shows Dan when he was younger playing {{W|Hamlet}} || Oh the critics they used to say, I was the new Olivier |- | Text on screen says "Best Actor" and it shows him getting an award || Thought I'd be the toast of Sundance, or maybe Cannes |- | Dan's Jungle Cruise boat floats across the screen || Ah, but don't bother trying to IMDB me, The only place you might possibly see me, Is riding my little boat around Adventureland, It ain't exactly what I planned but |- | Shows a fake snake in a tree || I'm a tour guide on the Jungle Cruise ride Skipper Dan is the name |- | Shows shows anamotronic figures of a rhino trying to get explorers who are climbing a tree || I'm a tour guide on the Jungle Cruise ride Skipper Dan is the name And I'm doing 34 shows every day, and every time it's the same |- | "Speed the Plow starring Dan" || I would've killed if I'd been in Speed-the-Plow But what's the difference that's all behind me now |- | Dan is "steering" the boat as people get on || 'Cause I'm paying the rent and I'm swallowing my pride And I'm working on the Jungle Cruise ride |- | Shows Dan acting in {{W|12 Angry Men}} || I should be there on Broadway, knocking 'em dead in 12 Angry Men |- | Dan is at the rhino section again and it fades to multiple different families that he's describing it to || But instead I'm here telling these lame jokes Again, and again, and again, and again, and again, and again, and again! |- | Shows a {{W|Bengal Tiger}} || Bengal tigers can jump over 20 feet... |- | Shows an elephant || That's an African Bull-Elephant... |- | Shows water || There it is. The backside of water! What have I done with my life? |- | Shows Dan's Grandfather with wings, as if he were an angel || I should've listened when my Grandfather said Why don't you major in business instead? |- | Dan and Ann, another Tour Guide, have their boats right next to each other. They pretend to shoot themselves in the head. || Now my hopes are vanished and my dreams have all died and I'll probably work forever as a tour guide on the Jungle Cruise ride |- | Shows a tiger and an elephant statue as Dans rides by || Skipper Dan is the name |- | Shows some snakes wading back and forth || And I'm doing 34 shows every day, and every time it's the same |- | Shows more hippos || Look at those hippos, they're wiggling their ears, somebody shoot me 'cause I'm bored to tears! |- | Shows a lady taking a picture of the alligators || Always said I'd be famous, I guess that I lied |- | Shows Dan getting his pictures taken with many people as it zooms in on his face || 'Cause I'm working on the Jungle Cruise ride I'm still working on the Jungle Cruise ride! |}
